{"title":"TRANSFUSIONES AMBULATORIAS Y PROCEDIMIENTOS TERAPÉUTICOS-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/TRANSFUSIONES AMBULATORIAS Y PROCEDIMIENTOS TERAPÉUTICOS-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"TRANSFUSIONES AMBULATORIAS Y\\NPROCEDIMIENTOS TERAPÉUTICOS","guid":"fvs2uXo4EJgR9nDz1qSkwg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## INTRODUCCIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"La transfusión de componentes sanguíneos apoya la terapia médica entregando al paciente glóbulos rojos, plaquetas,\\Nplasma y/o crioprecipitado para suplir necesidades y facilitar recuperación. La UMT realiza transfusiones ambulatorias\\Na pacientes adultos con estados deficitarios en tratamientos oncológicos, hematológicos y renales.","guid":"YtdRpd9CeiCxW4jRLF0ARQ","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"La sangría terapéutica (flebotomía) es un procedimiento indicado en enfermedades como hemocromatosis, policitemia vera y\\Nanemia sideroblástica hereditaria, consistente en extraer un volumen determinado de sangre según indicación médica.","guid":"jhxEttskEYQCPfZ-KAhgzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"0","text":"## OBJETIVOS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"- Informar al personal clínico sobre condiciones para atención de pacientes","guid":"DjWKy6_rgnSImBhkJ22t8g","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"- Detallar procedimiento de transfusión ambulatoria desde ingreso de solicitud hasta hemovigilancia","guid":"vphJDZBMtUkeiJKgek6hMQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"- Describir procedimiento de sangría terapéutica","guid":"nGuhxNy5aotTNHB4jZcW8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"## ALCANCE","guid":"","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"- Unidad de Medicina Transfusional HPM","guid":"6zZzHjUvFPKSaK8OdGAR2Q","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"- Servicios clínicos/Policlínicos que soliciten transfusión o flebotomía","guid":"dS6N0Uxl3n-9XUtzCxrhug","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"- Servicio de movilización","guid":"0mgZk0Ufe38FExjaC_I67A","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"8","text":"- Hospitales del área que envíen pacientes","guid":"gZwcqKz9zdnpGQtCLBKs4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"0","text":"## TRANSFUSIÓN\\NAMBULATORIA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"### Requisitos","guid":"gAtCQEWBc2NGVpRR5RXWHA","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"- Pacientes sin necesidad de terapias de apoyo (ECG, oxígeno)","guid":"16vBCfImUeuhuhl8LscbSw","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"- Compensados cardiovascularmente","guid":"WdMK-mJHNTariBm88JKIzA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"- Atención en horario hábil (L-J hasta 12h, V hasta 11h)","guid":"-6hvTnrmpx2vtyJIliB4sA","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"- Capacidad para 4 pacientes simultáneos (3 los martes por colectas)","guid":"-rOwzD2CVmaBjlHcUecbOA","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"- Medicación profiláctica indicada claramente","guid":"g_afDh0fUv_3GwrFmTm8qA","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"13","text":"### Procedimiento","guid":"9iq-EuoR3WGS_DeCX7QuFQ","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"1. Recepción del paciente y verificación de documentación","guid":"e6uzOiYjgyuNrCBj6iFLCQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"2. Verificación del consentimiento informado firmado","guid":"I2ndpJ4nZGrvH47rDohikw","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"3. Explicación del procedimiento","guid":"NQu6E_yxTF_Q2yqDW-J0fg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"4. Instalación de vía venosa periférica","guid":"Q_emPSz1H2kkuC0qRjU59Q","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"5. Toma de muestras si corresponde","guid":"SHf1fGbkYUIK1GBF-c702Q","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"6. Medición de signos vitales","guid":"WdXUAs8urWt0dE18CZFuBw","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"20","text":"7. Ingreso de solicitud al sistema e-Delphyn","guid":"UyRGRgu6e7KPWJKaMLGAsQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"20","text":"8. Selección de componentes","guid":"WnE3bdSSpUu2_ueMYmh80g","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"20","text":"9. Estudios inmunohematológicos si corresponde","guid":"j1IJTXJiwU_CT2YvlD_rVA","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"20","text":"10. Despacho de la transfusión","guid":"-DeVnPKWAA04fiR4FBs4Dg","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"20","text":"11. Completar Guía de seguridad transfusional","guid":"PFaKXYxV7ep-3a9De0csEQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"20","text":"12. Reclasificar al paciente a pie de cama","guid":"RcHH7DCvttjFRNQ-xLyZtw","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"20","text":"13. Registro de responsable, hora y signos vitales","guid":"bRqf3wiFaqVJrxxAsLbfhw","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"20","text":"14. Hemovigilancia durante todo el proceso","guid":"Bv6CltgUzvG6KlvFbbw7sg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"20","text":"15. Desconexión del equipo al finalizar","guid":"14R7nGx0KEWqz5PIIGZKug","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"20","text":"16. Medición de signos vitales","guid":"VfnGMdTzng8voLff-KAZ0g","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"20","text":"17. Retiro de vía venosa","guid":"p11ljSmVw-Gr-m8ZvpQb-w","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"20","text":"18. Vendaje compresivo","guid":"xTkMU3XibPh9OOhyAf3iNw","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"20","text":"19. Vigilancia post-transfusional (30 minutos mínimo)","guid":"-R46lP1emB-s2JEAwPixlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"13","text":"### Reacción Adversa","guid":"-OZXkpqN-eDQATpteBNZ2A","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"- Avisar al médico jefe de UMT","guid":"xdzoWexLmD7syHbBe8RNEA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"- Activar clave roja (#121) en ausencia del médico","guid":"4Vi3xOPaxMOFUTCgC6Mk-g","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"- Trasladar a emergencia","guid":"aVND99oFX9YxIgwIXWVCsA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"## SANGRÍAS\\NTERAPÉUTICAS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"### Requisitos","guid":"LrFT9V3sCDy4NCWdBAsKxQ","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"- Horario hábil (L-J hasta 16h, V hasta 15h)","guid":"aXJY7fMuU605chc7U4GOvQ","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"- Pacientes alimentados previamente","guid":"VRHb40XJric5hCs1b9ya4A","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"- Verificación de indicación médica (número, volumen, frecuencia)","guid":"UEQCC3HEzE8Yvl1JG7EJ6A","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"- Corroborar información con exámenes","guid":"4ng18p6TAXxn20BfYl17rw","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"44","text":"###\\NProcedimiento\\NTécnico","guid":"ayENBBGnstoEYsBam4pIdA","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"1. Acomodar al paciente","guid":"u4GY71Z1IAOW6OFLubstMQ","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"2. Tomar signos vitales","guid":"K01bmaXF6fn_kuXBMVYrWA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"3. Encender equipo de extracción","guid":"JjOjKY580rFUF35whP5UFg","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"4. Asepsia con alcohol 70%","guid":"zop1zd5rCWCTqTKmhRDyGg","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"50","text":"5. Preparar bolsa sobre balanza","guid":"aShRiyDpEjoMo8skRpIGdA","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"50","text":"6. Tarar la balanza","guid":"GHIKdglfkcdf7aHodDDtkQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"50","text":"7. Programar volumen de extracción","guid":"utYFjAHz9OA-QgF5bG5xwA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"50","text":"8. Realizar venopunción","guid":"3dEwbMEo91ZrvgN-kF0k0g","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"50","text":"9. Monitorizar extracción","guid":"_GCXR1rsEUdP9D6_rlwzZQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"50","text":"10. Control de signos vitales post-extracción","guid":"tOEzWlENwT8FLnGbZH-aFg","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"50","text":"11. Vendaje compresivo","guid":"7RokyQNPcMDtMy68GGAfZA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"50","text":"12. Rotular bolsa y registrar datos","guid":"YZFqZT_Oq2bKvr991iXSSQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"50","text":"13. Eliminar según protocolo","guid":"kP5sovvT-YzuIz2wXHY_PA","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"44","text":"### Cuidados\\NPosteriores","guid":"i0i9HTIaTZUTzftRyg4OIw","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"- Observación 15-20 minutos","guid":"RWhcZkQHmAXJaTjxFdD2fA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"- Hidratación adecuada (500cc previo)","guid":"wwmqUvRDmFGqw4Edvwh1Dw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"- Evitar esfuerzos el resto del día","guid":"OouIP36qnFQ3udfOlvvaGw","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"- Corroborar estado óptimo al finalizar","guid":"0QxmMeqrhTWsZotDNJOGEw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":68,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"TRANSFUSIONES AMBULATORIAS Y PROCEDIMIENTOS TERAPÉUTICOS-2025","id":"map_1095","resolved_references":[]}